Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:53.12,Rinon,,0,0,0,,Hai! Now we've started "{\i1}Houkago! Manande{\i0} Monday!" for this week. (Afterschool! Learning Monday!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:59.12,Rinon,,0,0,0,,This week's Day Leader is I, Isono Rinon. {\i1}Yoroshiku onegaishimasu!
